<p>Stephanie Clarkson is a fully qualified meditation teacher and hypnotherapist. An ex college lecturer, Steph turned to alternative approaches to heal her mind and body in a challenging time. After her own journey back to balanced health, she decided to retrain as a healing therapist with professional qualifications in hypnotherapy, life coaching, reiki, holistic therapist and hypnotherapy. She now helps others suffering from a wide range of physical and mental barriers.</p>
<p>Taking an holistic approach including meditation and mindfulness, those going through difficult periods can benefit from a range of spiritual or more traditional mental health approaches to find clarity, balance and a sense of peace.</p>
<p>Steph works both 1-to-1 and offers workshops and classes on her disciplines.</p>
